---
const WA = 'https://wa.me/584149189169';
const WA_TEXT = '?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20probar%20martes';
---
<section id="contacto" class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
      <span class="ve-eyebrow" data-c="t1">// 11 // Contacto</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="ve-title text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-sans font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-8 text-center" data-c="t1">
      Listo para <span class="font-black italic">dejar el caos</span>?
    </h2>
    <p class="ve-lead mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">Llena el formulario o escríbenos por WhatsApp. 30 minutos de conversación, sin compromiso.</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-6 mb-16">
      <a href="https://tudominio.larksuite.com/share/base/form/TULINKAQUI" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-ve-surface border border-ve-purple text-ve-purple hover:bg-ve-purple/10 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] transition-all text-sm">
        Llenar Formulario
        <svg class="ml-3 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
      </a>
      <a href={`${WA}${WA_TEXT}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-ve-purple text-white hover:bg-ve-purple-deep font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] transition-all text-sm shadow-lg"
         style="box-shadow: 0 8px 30px -8px rgba(124,58,237,0.5);">
        Hablar por WhatsApp
        <svg class="ml-3 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="ve-eyebrow" data-c="t5">
        Hecho en Venezuela · para Venezuela · con orgullo
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
